RentNGo

Car rental website. It offers features

  • for visitors, customers, and administrators, administrators can login and join to dashboard for defferent operation like manage contact, client, reservation, feed-back and cars.
  • Customer can signup and signin to access to dashboard for updating profile information, checking history of reservation and make new reservation if need and also for feed-back. RentNGo have also a navbar that facilaite navigating, for example Acceil, our cars, Faq, About, feed-back and contact.
  • Visitors easy access to RentNGo checking defferent function only when rent car or create feed-back or contact it should be login as costomer.

Spring boot, Angular, HTML, CSS, TypeScript, Bootstrap, Git, Github, StarUML, MYSQL,
